{"h07a49cc3g1979g45c2g9054gcec68a740234": ["*Screech!*", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "d19c91b4-1a5a-a8ec-03d5-4171eb0003e5"], "ha92aa58bgd189g40f1ga5cagde126e82281f": ["*Squeak. Squeak.*", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "2b973a75-43f8-ee20-c9ac-8e1ecd893d96"], "h42cbd950g4d6fg4e06g917eg9916b3f339e4": ["It hurts! It hurts!", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "1511394e-d16a-f7f5-d232-a7860dec43e8"], "h0c961513g0dd6g40e0g9557gbd4ee1f2090b": ["Please, make it stop!", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "d9faeb00-ac75-9a6d-6985-1e78f484976b"], "hc1a46212g06d3g4d65ga8b3g6297152dcb90": ["Slow down - what's wrong?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "b17c1f0f-f092-9a08-7faa-97f453d5ffbf"], "h0ca05957ga1fag45e1g8c4cge10476870e3f": ["Can't you hear it?", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "96f10689-0c0b-e098-1767-ddbca5e48a04"], "hef919254g3be4g4adag8625ged1327c76132": ["Her singing - it's awful!", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "bc7900b5-9690-3fe8-58c4-c7a2a9a212f0"], "h349bf543g1512g4eb4g9161g084b955d7c77": ["Terrible!", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "acf913dc-7972-df81-30e3-3b7b00bd923c"], "hc9c63b3cg5274g44f9g9f0egc1ba983c938b": ["It <i>is </i>quite a racket. You could just spare your ears by leaving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "a38c2baf-5f34-cdfc-63f5-946213e19b6c"], "hb2eb945fg953eg4d6cg8dfag01f50778e9d2": ["We can't! Our brains are melting!", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "adc5ac0b-f301-f3dd-2f4b-8a26a50ff856"], "h72f46df2ge12dg4e4cga7f5gf3f5d7436b37": ["Corinna, drag me away! The big one is right - we should go, before it's too late.", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "edd86559-883c-3f49-24ea-a93512258292"], "h8bc6b7b1g9c81g4e9dgbfd7g20262d695afb": ["With my last strength, I will save us both! Away. Away.", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "9438c05f-35cd-583d-e167-ee31d8c10eab"], "h7797e284gfc72g49e3gab4agf89aab6b4718": ["<i>Sing along with the bard - as loudly and off-key as you can.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "b0086a05-f618-1172-3c73-47dd2c0f3f84"], "h9f443027ge157g48e1ga2e4gb98302cb0fbd": ["Noooo!", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "82c71665-adbc-3189-1081-e4ee7551ca0a"], "hb187332ag9571g4d5fga845gf84404292e09": ["You're killing us!", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "597fb95b-5768-2530-82be-3952528c14c4"], "h2f496e64g3bedg446egbe56g6c7d1f8f3a61": ["My head is melting! I'm leaving before the damage is <i>permanent.</i>", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "a93445f3-f1e2-75b1-83d8-1f603d7f45c2"], "hcf4314fcg1704g4741ga205g7232965f5298": ["Don't mock her - she's trying her best... I assume.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "b8ee2697-ad35-1dc6-95c1-d88dfe7f3aac"], "haeffa3adg829eg49ddg8f7cgb30929a01379": ["Oh no! Whatever shall we do?", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "0a741719-546b-d36d-77d0-9bb1759e7b18"], "h495fd2f5g6831g4427gbf0cga11ddad448da": ["More witless creatures! More ear-bleed!", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "0ea369ac-076f-f96d-d7d0-d5ca1cb11cd3"], "hbe710521g7baeg4474gba98ge6d78f6b7009": ["Shhh - you're ruining the song.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "32a84455-6d11-0d56-c2c3-f181fe1993c8"], "h5ca53c60g4f57g4e12gadfdg614d5c19a812": ["Don't you think it's awful?", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "ffaa83fe-d928-ffe1-a7e0-ab8bb59fff4a"], "hf44d145dg506eg44a1ga47fg92d20f3abd99": ["We'll save you, poor soul.", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "9e5fd943-728c-6b3e-ec0f-03d4b8bd1948"], "h7d74d7c0g48bag4a50g938bg97327eb31b57": ["*The critters start a duet of their own, attempting to drown out the bard's music. They look at you expectantly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "c021322d-1dd5-d1f8-9b93-7c0347942d2e"], "he563c3bfga924g4692g9bf5gbb3fd321b16e": ["Bravo. You could go on tour, with talent like that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "87a57c3a-40b2-7678-7915-29cee542b85b"], "h28f848f2g48d4g48afgbe23g6acc58a0a892": ["Of course - we are born performers.", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "6fb40539-4e6b-02eb-b3aa-dd8df89b5c3e"], "hd5d1dd2dgb728g4024gb63agec0b39829c15": ["Unlike <i>some</i>. ", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "2fd25e41-f136-3a79-fc05-135ffc0060f0"], "h93fd05bbgeadbg4c8dg9d68g5cd60c9d08b3": ["<i>Sing along with them, improvising lyrics: 'How can we stop this dreadful song, this half-formed verse from leaden tongue?'</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "86ba5695-7715-21fc-6110-629ab14aa17b"], "h82234428g6550g4040gb6dag81f23a5f3a95": ["<i>Sing along with them, improvising lyrics: 'How can we stop this dreadful song, half-formed verse from devil's tongue?'</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "86ba5695-7715-21fc-6110-629ab14aa17b"], "h57d959e2g8873g4d65g83d8g00b7d24d4917": ["Yes, yes - that's it!", "efc0ba71-b3fa-4bb5-8a38-10bd0dd8b923", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "b034cfdf-1f6f-618b-b89d-66bcd86fc635"], "hb2f6feedg4ab3g41acgb693g7575c275183c": ["Finally, a song to set our heads straight after that <i>display. </i>We should leave, before the effect wears off.", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "cd1ca577-8a65-0219-964c-329679e97bea"], "h80966688g8f74g48d1gae18g86c798d9e3ba": ["Away, away!", "73f18550-4755-4e3c-9326-c328d34478af", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "7eab882a-cfdd-adfb-48c2-8fad54089228"], "h777c5b6agd3f2g47dagab74g19551b0fb12d": ["Shut up - I want to hear the bard.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "99fea8ba-5079-fe42-7d6d-868142059855"], "h84eeb8beg15efg48d9g9653g838e0a9222dd": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingBard_Animals.html", "2ad5b48f-de48-4c1e-48ae-76135bd22762"]}